OL,3,CMan who encouraged riot is first
OL,4,Cperson from Wales to be jailed over UK
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA man who encouraged people on social
OL,8,Fmedia to start a riot has become the
OL,9,Ffirst person from Wales to be
OL,10,Fconvicted and jailed amid the recent
OL,11,Funrest across the UK.
OL,13,FRichard Williams, 34, posted about
OL,14,Ftaking part in a riot and shared a
OL,15,Fderogatory meme about migrants in a
OL,16,Flocal Facebook group dedicated to
OL,17,Fprotests, the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService (CPS) said.
