OL,7,FJenny Hopkins, chief crown prosecutor
OL,8,Ffor CPS Cymru/Wales, said: "Williams
OL,9,Fwrongly thought that he could spread
OL,10,Fderogatory and menacing content from
OL,11,Fbehind a computer screen.
OL,13,F"Despite not taking part in unrest
OL,14,Fhimself, he used social media to
OL,15,Fencourage others to engage in violent
OL,16,Fbehaviour.
